description.narrative: Effective coordination is critical for the successful nutrition service delivery. UNICEF supported two coordination meetings; the national salt iodisation (IDD) task force meeting and the IMAM technical working group meeting. The IDD quarterly meeting brought together salt producers and traders and national authorities responsible for the regulation of salt iodisation in the country. The meeting provided feedback on the inspection and quality monitoring of the salt iodisation and the challenges to overcome. The IMAM technical working group meeting was also a quarterly technical coordination meeting to discuss progress and challenges of the treatment of acute malnutrition programme. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/12/2019
